2_474 ataH vidyateː mahAːBAːrateː zloːkaH - .
2_475 na deːvAː daNxamAːdAːya rakSanti pazupAːlavat .
2_476 yaM tu rakSitumicCanti buDdayAː saMyoːjayanti tam .
2_477 vijYAːnasya vikAːseːna yAːni upaBoːgasAːDanAːni yAːni ca anyAːni aneːkAːni upakaraNAːni prakRteːH anukampayAː asmAːBiH upalabDAːni tEːH sarvEːH asmAːkaM jIːvanaM suKasampannaM saMjAːtam .
2_478 parameːtasyAːM prakriyAːyAːm asmAːBiH paryAːvaraNasya mahatIː hiMsAː kRtAː .
2_479 eːtadatiriktaM svAːvazyakatAːH pUːrayituM vanAːnAːM sTAːneː BavanAːni ,yantrazAːlAːH nUːtanAːzca mAːrgAːH asmAːBiH nirmIːyanteː .
2_480 eːteːna grAːmAːNAːmapi paryAːvaraNasya svAːBAːvikatAː naSqAː nagarAːNAːM tu kAː kaTAː .
2_481 moːqarayAːnEːH yantrazAːlAːnAːM ca avaziSqEːH viSAːktapadAːrTEːH BUːmiH jalaM vAːyuzca -sarvaM paryAːvaraNaM dUːSitaM saMjAːtam .
2_482 vanAːnAːM vRkSAːNAːM ca pAːtaneːna jalam avazoːSayituM samarTAː na Bavati .
2_483 eːteːna heːtunAː nidAːGoː varDateː .
2_484 eːkasmin samayeː ativRSqiH tayAː jalAːplAːvaH teːna ca mahatIː hAːniH Bavati .
2_485 aparasmin samayeː anAːvRSqiH tayAː ca durBikSaM Aːpadyateː .
2_486 samAːsataH eːtatkaTayituM zakyateː yat paryAːvaraNasya eːtAːvatIː hAːniH kRtAː yayAː Aːsanneː eːva BaviSyati kAːleː zudDaM jalaM zudDazca vAːyuH durlaBoː BaviSyati .
