2_489 BUːmeːH, jalasya, vAːyoːH, prAːNinAːM, vanaspatIːnAːM,vanAːnAːM ca surakSAː asmAːkaM paramameːva karttavyam .
2_490 svacCasya paryAːvaraNasya svasTasya ca jIːvanasya kRteː vayaM yAːni yAːvanti ca vastUːni upaBoːgAːya prakRteːH prAːpnumaH tAːni sarvAːNi prakRtiM pratyAːvartayituM tatparAː Baveːma .
2_491 vanAːnAːmupaBoːgeːna teːSAːM yAː nyUːnatAː asmAːBiH kriyateː tAːM pUːrayituM vayaM ca sAːvaDAːnAːH sannadDAːzca Baveːma .
2_492 eːtatkRteː grAːmeːSu nagareːSu ca asmAːBiH AːzuvarDanazIːlAːH pAːdapAːH AːroːpaNIːyAːH .
