2_494 eːtAːdRzIː dRSqiH sarveːSAːM kalyAːNAːya BaviSyati .
2_495 SoːxaSaH pAːVaH.
2_496 kasmin-cit jalAːzayeː anAːgataviDAːtAː, pratyupannamatiH yadBaviSyazceːti trayaH matsyAːH avasan .
