2_500 tadanantaram teːSAːm vacanam zrutvAː teːSu matsyeːSu anAːgataviDAːtAː nAːma matsyaH akaTayat- zvaH praBAːta-samayeː teː DIːvarAːH atra AːgamiSyanti sarvAːn ca matsyAːn jAːleː badDvAː neːzyanti .
