2_545 prasidDasya kvIːnsa kAːleːja- nAːmakasya saMskRta-mahAːvidyAːlayasya dIːptimAːn CAːtraH candrazeːKaraH rAːSqraM prati AːtmAːnaM samarpitavAːn AːsIːt .
2_546 jAːliyan~vAːlAː- kAːNxeː AːwglazAːsanasya nRzaMsatAːM zrutvAː vicalitaH san tasmAːt krUːrazAːsanAːt deːzasya muktayeː teːna sawkalpaH kRtaH .
2_547 sazastrasya sawgrAːmasya kRteː DanasawgrahAːrTam anyEːH sahayoːgiBiH saha AːjAːdaH kAːkoːrIː nAːmakeː sTAːneː rAːjakIːyakoːSam apahRtavAːn .
2_548 lAːlAːlAːjapatarAːya- mahoːdayasya GAːtakaH sEːNxarsa- nAːmakaH AːwglaH tEːH krAːntikAːriBiH nihataH .
2_549 keːndriya-viDAːnasaBAːyAːm eːteːSAːM visPoːqaneːna AːwglazAːsanamapi BayAːkrAːntaM jAːtam .
2_550 parantu ahoː, kAːlasya kuqilAː gatiH ! eːkamnavatriNieːkam IːsavIːyasya ParavarIː - mAːsasya dvAːviMzatamaH divasaH Bavati sma .
